You found your own style?

41
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,480
Whatever.

42
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:37,680
What I used before was too troublesome.

43
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,960
From now on,

44
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,600
I’ll be me.

45
