I’ll dress myself however I like.

46
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:02,080
(Result of Nanfeng No. 1 High School Physics Contest)
Jiang Haoyue has won three rounds.

47
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:04,040
When can we go on the autumn trip?

48
